name: FChaosCollisionEventRequestSettings
doc: Settings used to define collision event requests

MaxNumberResults: The maximum number of results to return.
MinMass: The minimum mass threshold for the results (compared with min of particle 1 mass and particle 2 mass).
MinSpeed: The min speed threshold for the results (compared with min of particle 1 speed and particle 2 speed).
MinImpulse: The minimum impulse threshold for the results.
MaxDistance: The maximum distance threshold for the results.
SortMethod: The method used to sort the collision events.
